561
00:38:13,625 --> 00:38:14,957
Kill him!

562
00:38:49,333 --> 00:38:50,874
Six Paths Reincarnation...

563
00:38:51,208 --> 00:38:52,541
evil ghosts shall be punished!

564
00:38:59,750 --> 00:39:00,999
Open your eyes and look...

565
00:39:01,000 --> 00:39:03,416
this is where you belong.

566
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:27,999
The eternity you pursue...

567
00:39:28,583 --> 00:39:31,041
relies on sucking the essence and blood of others.

568
00:39:35,500 --> 00:39:36,624
But my Human Race...

569
00:39:37,083 --> 00:39:39,124
has thrived for tens of millions of years...

570
00:39:39,583 --> 00:39:40,832
not through slaughter...

571
00:39:41,417 --> 00:39:41,957
but through the resilience...

572
00:39:41,958 --> 00:39:44,166
passed down through generations.

573
00:39:50,125 --> 00:39:52,416
How can I allow you fiends...

574
00:39:52,417 --> 00:39:53,999
to sever the roots of my civilization?

575
00:40:30,375 --> 00:40:31,999
Your sins are heavy...

576
00:40:32,750 --> 00:40:34,832
you owe a debt of blood...

577
00:40:35,167 --> 00:40:36,457
go to hell...

578
00:40:36,833 --> 00:40:38,499
and repay it slowly!

579
00:41:06,875 --> 00:41:07,999
So that's how it is.

580
00:41:08,833 --> 00:41:10,832
The Six Paths contain the true killing intent of the Six Paths.

581
00:41:11,333 --> 00:41:13,041
This fist technique is truly domineering.

582
00:41:14,708 --> 00:41:15,582
Alone against many demons...

583
00:41:15,583 --> 00:41:16,707
just watching the Saint...

584
00:41:16,958 --> 00:41:18,541
makes my blood boil.

585
00:41:18,750 --> 00:41:20,416
Never expected...

586
00:41:21,250 --> 00:41:22,250
the Human Race...

587
00:41:22,750 --> 00:41:25,332
to still have such combat strength in this world.

588
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:27,207
Retreat.

589
00:41:29,167 --> 00:41:31,791
You are not his match.

590
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:44,000
Human...

591
00:41:44,583 --> 00:41:46,041
You are strong.

592
00:41:46,042 --> 00:41:47,416
Extremely strong.

593
00:41:47,417 --> 00:41:49,041
Terrifyingly strong.

594
00:41:49,792 --> 00:41:50,874
But today...

595
00:41:51,458 --> 00:41:52,916
Ziwei Star...

596
00:41:53,708 --> 00:41:55,249
will surely be destroyed.

597
00:42:01,083 --> 00:42:02,083
Bad...

598
00:42:02,292 --> 00:42:03,957
That multi-armed monster has awakened!

599
00:42:04,625 --> 00:42:06,582
Even if I die here today...

600
00:42:07,208 --> 00:42:08,791
you, a ship full of Ancient Kings...

601
00:42:09,250 --> 00:42:10,749
will be buried with me!

602
00:42:11,083 --> 00:42:12,624
Annihilated completely!

603
00:42:14,917 --> 00:42:16,749
Lowly Human Race...

604
00:42:17,583 --> 00:42:20,416
yet you dare be so rampant despite being our former food?

605
00:42:20,417 --> 00:42:22,499
Insolent!

606
00:43:29,750 --> 00:43:31,832
Senior is trading injury for injury...

607
00:43:31,833 --> 00:43:32,833
with the Thousand-Hand God-Demon!

608
00:43:47,875 --> 00:43:49,832
Break, all of you!

609
00:43:55,042 --> 00:43:56,082
Die!

610
00:44:01,583 --> 00:44:05,167
Thousand Hands Shatter Soul Art!

611
00:44:15,833 --> 00:44:16,499
Bad...

612
00:44:16,500 --> 00:44:17,500
The formation is broken!

613
00:44:44,167 --> 00:44:44,999
These Ancient Creatures...

614
00:44:45,000 --> 00:44:46,624
each has the cultivation of the First Heaven of the Immortal Platform.

615
00:44:46,833 --> 00:44:48,374
I need to find a way to repair the formation...

616
00:44:48,667 --> 00:44:50,541
to buy Senior a sliver of opportunity.

617
00:45:00,375 --> 00:45:01,874
The Mother Qi of All Things is heavy as a mountain...

618
00:45:01,875 --> 00:45:02,875
unbreakable.

619
00:45:03,000 --> 00:45:04,249
Although my current cultivation is insufficient...

620
00:45:04,792 --> 00:45:06,207
the Mother Qi is a sacred item of the Great Emperor...

621
00:45:06,458 --> 00:45:07,832
perhaps I can use the Cauldron to try!

622
00:45:08,250 --> 00:45:09,582
Don't come any closer!

623
00:45:15,542 --> 00:45:16,707
Human...

624
00:45:17,250 --> 00:45:19,582
You are a respectable opponent.

625
00:45:21,000 --> 00:45:23,624
But the rising trend of my race...

626
00:45:24,000 --> 00:45:25,666
cannot be stopped by anyone.

627
00:45:30,625 --> 00:45:32,916
Four Symbols Tribulation Annihilation!

628
00:45:33,542 --> 00:45:35,916
Burial of your Human Race's destiny!

629
00:45:43,792 --> 00:45:45,582
Just die!

630
00:46:11,566 --> 00:46:13,566
[Shrouding the Heavens: Mini Knowledge Guide]

631
00:46:13,887 --> 00:46:48,466
[Taigu Clan Cultivation Realms (Ancient Race Realm System)- The Taigu clans cultivate through a mysterious system similar to that of humans,
but the names used for each realm are different. Because the Taigu era is far too ancient, no one can clearly explain the exact names of the realms today. People only roughly know that when members of the Taigu clans reach the realm equivalent to Immortal Platform (Xiantai), they are honored as “Kings.” Among the powerful beings of ancient times, some were also called Kings, while others were known as Ancestor Kings. Just how powerful these Kings truly were remains uncertain; some speculate they were comparable to the ancient Sages.]

632
00:46:48,490 --> 00:47:11,290
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

